FBIS3-12819 "drnes044dd_94012" FBIS-NES-94-044 Document Type:Daily Report 7 Mar 1994 Palestinian Affairs Hamas Warns Settlers To Leave Before 15 Mar JN0703131594 Paris Radio Monte Carlo in Arabic 1210 GMT 7 Mar 94 JN0703131594 Paris Radio Monte Carlo Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] The 'Izz al-Din al-Qassam Battalions, the military wing of the Islamic Resistance Movement, Hamas today addressed a final warning to Jewish settlers to leave their settlements. In a statement distributed in the occupied territories, it set 15 March as the deadline for this evacuation. The statement, which is signed by the command of 'Izz al-Din al-Qassam Battalions, says that it has decided to reply militarily through five stages, and that each stage will make the Israeli people and settlers weep over their dead.
